Type h and press enter to open the Edway Users Manual with your favorite
browser.  Be sure the BROWSER environment variable contains your browser's
name. Type h, a space, and a command name, or a command line option,
to get help with that command or option.  Type h, a space, and h, to
get help with the help command.  Type h, a space, and an unrecognized
entry for still further information.

